      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
