    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once starting to soften, add the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>remaining soy sauce </strong>to the pan with the <strong>cooked rice </strong>and <strong>blanched peas</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
